  <summary>4/26/1999--Introduced.
Prevention of School Violence Act of 1999 - Establishes the National Commission on the Prevention of School Violence. Directs the Commission to submit a final report to the President and the Congress within one year after its first meeting. Terminates the Commission 60 days after such required report date.</summary>
